The moſt Ancient and Noble Families of Europe are declining;
but eſpecially here not far remote, or in England: And
this Saturn by Retrogradation doth eaſily declare.

My friend, be quiet, thou art not the man, thy time is ſhort;
the Chicken of the Weſt ſhall prevail: Return in peace, if thou
canſt, to the Sepulchre of thy not-Kingly Anceſtours, &c.
